param.description:
filters, e.g.:


filters = {<object> --> {"pose", "jointPosition", "layer"}, sim.scene --> {"engineProperties"}}


filters = {<object1> --> {}, <object2> --> {"pose"}}


filters = {"sceneObject" --> {"pose"}, "shape" --> {"position"}}

method.description:
Writes an image to the vision sensor (and applies any image processing via the
vision callback functions
). The vision sensor should be flagged as external input
